		<h2>Rating Guidelines</h2>
		<p>Whene rating tweets, please keep this benchmark in mind:</p>
		<br>
		<div id="star-benchmark">
			<p>
				<b><span>&#9733; &#9733; &#9733;</span> Three Stars</b><br>
				Top tweets that absolutely must make it into the book.
			</p>
			<p>
				<b><span>&#9733; &#9733;</span> Two Stars</b><br>
				Anything from good to great.
			</p>
			<p>
				<b><span>&#9733;</span> One Stars</b><br>
				Noteworthy tweet that deserves to be considered.
			</p>
			<p>
				<b>Zero Stars</b><br>
				Not interesting enough to consider it for any chapter.
			</p>
		</div>
		<p>When in doubt, give it a star or it might be forgotten.</p>
	</div>
